descript.abstract: This dataset represents a selected set of information that was collected for the 2007 Census of Agriculture by the National Agricultural Statistics Service, U.S. Department of Agriculture. There are 25 categories of data which include information about farms, crops, livestock, values of products, and farm operator characteristics. The data is for the United States and is presented by county. This is a replacement for the June 2005 Agriculture Census of the United States ? 2002 map layer.
descript.purpose: This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
descript.supplinf: The complete information for the 2007 Census of Agriculture is available from the National Agricultural Statistics Service, U.S. Department of Agriculture, <http://www.agcensus.usda.gov/>. Data for additional years are available from the same site.

attracc.attraccr: Attribute information remains the same as given by the author of the data. However, when information is missing or ambiguous, the GIS Information Systems Center at Tufts University researches other metadata sources for explanations. If sufficient information is unavailable, "unknown attribute" is given as the definition. If the attribute has been created through a geoprocessing function, "geoprocessed identifier" is given. If the attribute is known, but the values are not, "unknown" is given for values. Features' units of measurement are determined if not already given.

dataqual.logic: The map layer was checked for topological consistency using the ArcGIS command BUILD. No other checks for logical consistency were performed on this map layer.
dataqual.complete: This map layer includes 25 categories from the National Agricultural Statistics Service, U.S. Department of Agriculture's 2007 Census of Agriculture data. It is based on county data for all 50 States.

procstep.procdesc: Atlas_Cnty2001 which is a map layer containing 2001 county boundaries for the United States, and AG-CENSUS2007 .dbf files were loaded into ArcMap. Tables were joined using the Fips attribute. New attribute fields were added for each .dbf and field calculations were made for each attribute field. The join was then removed.

>Defined projection (NAD 1983) >Imported metadata from provided agcensp020.txt (arcgis 9.3) >Changed citation title from "agcensp020" to "Agriculture Census USA 2007" >Changed access contraints from "None" to "Unrestricted Access Online" >Changed name of file from "agcensp020" to "USAagcensus07" >Substituted "United States. Dept. of Agriculture" for "National Atlas of the United States" as the originator >Added Larger Work Citation >Added theme keyword "polygon" to added theme keyword thesaurus "FGDC" >Added LCSH theme keywords >Added GNIS and GNS place keywords >Replaced Tufts as the distributor >Exported metadata
